<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Login - Steam Clone</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 400px; margin-top: 100px; text-align: center;">
        <h2>로그인</h2>
        <form action="/login" method="POST">
            <input type="text" name="username" placeholder="아이디" required>
            <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="비밀번호" required>
            <button type="submit" style="width: 100%;">로그인 하기</button>
        </form>
        <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 13px;">
            계정이 없으신가요? <a href="/signup" style="color: #66c0f4;">회원가입</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
